high_descs: Take a step to the left and face the counter in front of the microwave.
Pick up the spatula on the counter.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the stove.
Place the spatula on the back left burner on the stove.
Pick up the pan on the stove with the knife in it.
Step to the right to face the white table.
Place the pan with the knife in it on the white table.
anns.task_desc: To put a knife in a pan and set it on the white table.

high_descs: Go to the left of the coffee machine.
Pick up the spatula on the top on the table in front of the coffee maker.
Turn around and go to the stove in the corner.
Place the spatula in the square pan on the left back burner.
Pick up the pan with the spatula in it.
Turn right and go to the front of the white table on the left.
Place the pan with knife in it on the table on the left of the liquid soap.
anns.task_desc: Put the pan with the spatula in it on the table.

high_descs: Take a step to the left to face the coffee machine.
Pick up the spatula from the left side of the coffee machine.
Carry the spatula and turn around and to find the stove.
Place the spatula in the pan on the back left burner.
Pick up the pan from the burner.
Carry the pan and turn around and to the left. Face the white table on the left.
Place the pan and spatula on the left side of the white table.
anns.task_desc: Move a pan and spatula to a table.
